			<p outputclass="List3" class="- topic/p ">(ii)  The Contractor shall not submit payment requests more frequently than monthly.</p>
			<p outputclass="List3" class="- topic/p ">(iii)  Incurred cost is determined by the Contractor’s accounting books and records, which the contractor shall provide access to upon request of the Contracting Officer for the administration of this clause.</p>
